islike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"環首刀係漢代就有，明代有借鑑倭刀既雙手戚家刀，一般黎講係黎對付扎甲，歐洲劍細長係因為歐洲板甲既出現需要劈刺攻擊弱點譬如腋下"},{"pid":"20b7c618ba83c7f7f24b59255fd639264460d3f9","tid":409543,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中國用開石仔</blockquote><br />\n都有，但似乎投石步兵喺有牧羊人文化嘅地方會常見啲</blockquote><br />\n最近解放軍對印度都有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔清楚印中衝突嘅具體情況，但應該同古代投石兵嘅情況唔同<br />\n<br />\nbtw，投石幾型"},{"pid":"8691e06aa89ae5ef60beafb5bd525d07995fffe3","tid":409543,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"十九世紀歐洲好多騎兵都係用刀同長槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb42c2433bbb50882cf8d6b7c2965fdf81464fcc","tid":409543,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中國唔係用劍咩？</blockquote><br />\n都有</blockquote><br />\n下層士兵用刀，刀主要用黎劈，岩晒d冇訓練既士兵用，夠簡單</blockquote><br />\n劈先難學，發力同伸展已經唔易<br />\n<br />\n日本戰國同古代中原下層士兵普遍使用長武器就真"},{"pid":"5a5d48f3e0e339797f4063609e3032947fb8f9b9","tid":409543,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環首刀係漢代就有，明代有借鑑倭刀既雙手戚家刀，一般黎講係黎對付扎甲，歐洲劍細長係因為歐洲板甲既出現需要劈刺攻擊弱點譬如腋下</blockquote><br />\n日本刀（包埋中國山寨嘅戚家刀、單刀、苗刀等）唔係用嚟對付著甲者，<br />\n亦好難想像點用細劍攻擊全身板甲嘅弱點"},{"pid":"d50d9c4b1a94ed0cbe32b5b6b4249c9e590ce63e","tid":409543,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Grosse Messer算唔算你所講嘅「大刀」<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://www.coldsteel.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/thumbnail/960x/17f82f742ffe127f42dca9de82fb58b1/8/8/88gmsm.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coldsteel.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F1%2Fthumbnail%2F960x%2F17