ke":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Grosse Messer算唔算你所講嘅「大刀」<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://www.coldsteel.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/thumbnail/960x/17f82f742ffe127f42dca9de82fb58b1/8/8/88gmsm.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coldsteel.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F1%2Fthumbnail%2F960x%2F17f82f742ffe127f42dca9de82fb58b1%2F8%2F8%2F88gmsm.jpg&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNT5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fe7cd2df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.coldsteel.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/thumbnail/960x/17f82f742ffe127f42dca9de82fb58b1/8/8/88gmsm.jpg</a>&quot;  /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺好靚，但cold steel出，唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCokd steel 已經算比較平</blockquote><br />\n我窮，對我嚟講taobao先叫平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dcbb22859931520171f59450eb85b83fbf4597","tid":409543,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環首刀係漢代就有，明代有借鑑倭刀既雙手戚家刀，一般黎講係黎對付扎甲，歐洲劍細長係因為歐洲板甲既出現需要劈刺攻擊弱點譬如腋下</blockquote><br />\n日本刀（包埋中國山寨嘅戚家刀、單刀、苗刀等）唔係用嚟對付著甲者，<br />\n亦好難想像點用細劍攻擊全身板甲嘅弱點</blockquote><br />\n有對付著甲<br />\n又有對付唔著甲<br />\n不過對付著甲唔係好似卡通咁斬開副甲<br />\n而係專斬無甲的部位<br />\n腋下、大腿內側、面部下面斬上去"},{"pid":"2a23a9e1b5b251b3ff40d383b54d78b0f3d1fa2f","tid":409543,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環首刀係漢代就有，明代有借鑑倭刀既雙手戚家刀，一般黎講係黎對付扎甲，歐洲劍細長係因為歐洲板甲既出現需要劈刺攻擊弱點譬如腋下</blockquote><br />\n日本刀（包埋中國山寨嘅戚家刀、單刀、苗刀等）唔係用嚟對付著甲者，<br />\n亦好難想像點用細劍攻擊全身板甲嘅弱點</blockquote><br />\n板甲連結處"},{"pid":"6f575ac7ff3dc3e2911df831440501683cfa04c2","tid":409543,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:36:3